    * Affirming Anglican Catholicism
    * Agility Association of Canada
    * Alameda Arts Council
    * American Airlines Center
    * American Anglican Council
    * Amphibian Airplanes of Canada
    * Army Air Corps of the British Army
    * Associação Académica de Coimbra (Portuguese for "Coimbra's Academic Association")
          o Associação Académica de Coimbra - O.A.F. (AAC/OAF - Football Team)
    * Atlanta Athletic Club
    * Augmentative and Alternative Communication